  <h1>Gitea Mirror Quick Start Guide</h1>
  
  <p>This guide will help you get Gitea Mirror up and running quickly.</p>
  
  <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
  
  <p>Before you begin, make sure you have:</p>
  
  <ol>
    <li>A GitHub account with a personal access token</li>
    <li>A Gitea instance with an access token</li>
    <li>Docker and docker-compose (recommended) or Node.js 18+ installed</li>
  </ol>
  
  <h2>Installation</h2>
  
  <h3>Using Docker (Recommended)</h3>
  
  <ol>
    <li>
      <p>Clone the repository:</p>
      <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/arunavo4/gitea-mirror.git
cd gitea-mirror</code></pre>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Start the application in production mode:</p>
      <pre><code>docker-compose --profile production up -d</code></pre>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Access the application at http://localhost:4321</p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</main>
